:: National Holidays
: New Year's Day                                  public on january 1                                                "رأس السنة"
: Worker's day                                    public on may 1                                                   "عيد العمّال"
: Martyrs' Day                                    public on may 6                                                  "عيد الشهداء"
: Liberation and Resistance Day                   public on may 25                                      "عيد المقاومة و التحرير"
: Lebanese Independence Day                       public on november 22                                            "عيد الإستقلال"

:: Religious Holidays
: Aremenian Christmas                             public religious on january 6                    "عيد الميلاد - الأرمن الأرثودكس"
: St. Maroun Day                                  public religious on february 9                                 "عيد مار مارون"
: Good Friday (Western Church)                    public religious on april 19                "(الطوائف الغربية) الجمعة العظيمة"
: Easter Sunday (Western Church)                  public religious on april 22                  "(الطوائف الغربية) الفصح المجيد"
: Good Friday (Eastern Church)                    public religious on april 26               "(الطوائف الشرقية) الجمعة العظيمة"
: Easter Sunday (Eastern Church)                  public religious on april 29                  "(الطوائف الشرقية) الفصح المجيد"
: Eid al-Fitr                                     public religious on may 5                                          "عيد الفطر"
: Eid al-Adha                                     public religious on july 30                                        "عيد الأضحى"
: Feast of the Assumption                         public religious on august 15                             "عيد إنتقال العذراء"
: Islamic New year                                public religious on august 31                              "رأس السنة الهجرية"
: Day of Ashura                                   public religious on september 10                                "ذكرى عاشوراء"
: Mawlid                                          public religious on november 10                                   "مولد النبي"
: Christmas                                       public religious on december 25                                   "عيد الميلاد"

